: Django&nbsp;自带的ORM，用于设计数据库表。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| ---&nbsp;tests.py&nbsp; :&nbsp; 用于编写Django单元测试。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| ---&nbsp;veiws.py ：视图文件，用于编写功能的主要处理逻辑。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	4、修改配置文件\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	打开settings.py&nbsp;配置文件，添加blog应用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	INSTALLED_APPS=[\'django.contrib.admin\',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\'django.contrib.auth\',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\'django.contrib.contenttypes\',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\'django.contrib.sessions\',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\'django.contrib.messages\',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\'django.contrib.staticfiles\',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\'blog\',&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	]\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	配置mysql\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	使用pymysql连接数据\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	import pymysql<br />\r\npymysql.install_as_MySQLdb()<br />\r\n设置数据库账号、密码\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	DATABASES = {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 环境搭建比较简单，不再详细介绍，网上很多教程可以参考\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t2、创建django项目\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; 使用django-admin创建django项目\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;django-admin startproject blog_project\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp;cd&nbsp;blog_project\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp;这样就可以创建一个简单的django项目\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t3、创建app\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;python manage.py startapp blog\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; 在blog目录下会生成views.py、admin.py、models.py、tests.py&nbsp;等文件\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| --- admin.py&nbsp; :&nbsp; django&nbsp;自带admin后面管理，将models.py&nbsp;中表映射到后台。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| ---&nbsp;models.py&nbsp; : Django&nbsp;自带的ORM，用于设计数据库表。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| ---&nbsp;tests.py&nbsp; :&nbsp; 用于编写Django单元测试。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| ---&nbsp;veiws.py ：视图文件，用于编写功能的主要处理逻辑。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t4、修改配置文件\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t打开settings.py&nbsp;配置文件，添加blog应用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tINSTALLED_APPS=['django.contrib.admin',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'django.contrib.auth',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'django.contrib.contenttypes',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'django.contrib.sessions',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'django.contrib.messages',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'django.contrib.staticfiles',\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;'blog',&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t]\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t配置mysql\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t使用pymysql连接数据\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\timport pymysql<br />\r\npymysql.install_as_MySQLdb()<br />\r\n设置数据库账号、密码\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tDATABASES = {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 'default': {<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 'ENGINE': 'django.db.backends.mysql',<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 'NAME': 'blogdbs',<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 'USER': 'root',<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 可以看到数据库中生成了对应的表\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; 创建管理员账号密码\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; python manage.py createsuperuser\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t6、启动\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; 访问localhost:8000/admin 就可以登录后台进行管理\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br />\r\n</p>", 0, False, '2018-08-06 04:09:54.359630', 1, 1]
